CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Multi Ways Holdings Ltd is a supplier of a wide range of heavy construction equipment for sales and rental in Singapore and the surrounding region. The wide variety of new and used heavy construction equipment for sale and rental by customers range from: earth-moving equipment such as bulldozers, off-terrain dump trucks, excavators and wheel loaders; material-handling equipment such as crawler cranes, rough terrain cranes, scissor lifts, forklifts, boom-lifts and telescopic handlers; road-building equipment such as motor graders, vibrating compactors, asphalt finishers, skid loaders, backhoe loaders, hand rollers and mini excavators; and generators and compressors, such as air compressors, generators, lighting towers and welding machines.
